<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-03-25T04:44:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-03-25T04:44:00-05:00" n="445" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d445">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">882.7962/75: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Wharton</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Monrovia</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-03-25T09:00:00-00:44">March 25,
                                    1942—9 a.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received 3:50 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>100. From McBride for Villard. If agreement is not yet approved please
                            phone John Martyn, assistant to Secretary of War and ask him to give the
                            Secretary following personal message from me: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                <p>I would be grateful if War Department could approve agreement
                                    with Liberia which I have negotiated and inform Department of
                                    State. Delay is weakening our position here. Many thanks.</p>
                            </quote>
                        </p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed> [McBride] <lb/>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Wharton</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>